Class MySqlDdlParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.debezium.relational.ddl.AbstractDdlParser
      • io.debezium.relational.ddl.LegacyDdlParser
        • io.debezium.connector.mysql.MySqlDdlParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DdlParser

    @NotThreadSafe
public class MySqlDdlParser
extends LegacyDdlParser
    A parser for DDL statements.

    See the MySQL SQL Syntax documentation for the grammar supported by this parser.

        protected void parseDefaultClause(TokenStream.Marker start)

        Parameters:
        start - the marker at the beginning of the clause
